<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Single Product Page</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Resource1.css">
</head>

<body class="background-r1">
    <div class="Navbar">

        <nav>
            <img src="~/imgBia/Screenshot_2024-05-07_185200-removebg-preview.png" class="logo">
         
        </nav>
    </div>



    <section class="product-container">
         @* left side *@
        <div class="img-card">
            <img src="~/imgBia/chair1.jpg" alt="" id="featured-image">
            @*  small img *@
            <div class="small-Card">
                <img src="~/imgBia/chair1.2.jpg" alt="" class="small-Img">

                <img src="~/imgBia/chair1.4.jpg" alt="" class="small-Img">
                <img src="~/imgBia/chair1.jpg" alt="" class="small-Img">
            </div>
             @* Right side  *@
            <div class="product-info">
                <h3>Classic Chair</h3>
                <h5>Price: $100 <del>$200</del></h5>
                <p>Introducing our Classic Event Chairs, the epitome of elegance and functionality for any occasion. Crafted with precision and style in mind, these chairs are designed to elevate the ambiance of your event while ensuring comfort for your guests. Constructed with durable materials, our White Event Chairs are not only visually striking but also sturdy and reliable, capable of withstanding the demands of any gathering. The sleek white finish adds a touch of sophistication, seamlessly complementing any décor scheme.</p>
                <p>
                    Introducing our Classic Event Chairs, the epitome of elegance and functionality for any occasion. Crafted with precision and style in mind, these chairs are designed to elevate the ambiance of your event while ensuring comfort for your guests. Constructed with durable materials, our White Event Chairs are not only visually striking but also sturdy and reliable, capable of withstanding the demands of any gathering. The sleek white finish adds a touch of sophistication, seamlessly complementing any décor scheme.  Featuring a ergonomic design, these chairs provide optimal support for prolonged seating, allowing your guests to relax and enjoy the festivities with ease. Whether it's a wedding, corporate event, or gala dinner, our White Event Chairs are the perfect choice to make a lasting impression on your attendees.
                </p>

                <div class="Colour">
                    <p>Colour:</p>
                    <select name="Colour" id="Colour" class="Colour-option">
                        <option value="Black">Black</option>
                        <option value="White">White</option>
                        <option value="Cream">Cream</option>

                    </select>
                </div>

                <div class="quantity">
                    <input type="number" value="1" min="1">
                    <button>Add to Event</button>
                </div>

                <div>
                    <p>Delivery:</p>
                    <p>Free standard shipping on orders over $35 before tax, plus free returns.</p>
                    <div class="delivery">
                        <p>TYPE</p> <p>HOW LONG</p> <p>HOW MUCH</p>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="delivery">
                        <p>Standard delivery</p>
                        <p>1-4 business days</p>
                        <p>$4.50</p>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="delivery">
                        <p>Express delivery</p>
                        <p>1 business day</p>
                        <p>$10.00</p>
                    </div>
                    <hr>
                    <div class="delivery">
                        <p>Pick up in store</p>
                        <p>1-3 business days</p>
                        <p>Free</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
    </section>

  @*  script tags  *@
    <script src="/js/product_page.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
